data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bath haven where comfort and style are harmonious! Natural light bathes the spacious living room through newer windows, accentuating the inviting laminate wood flooring that seamlessly extends into the separate dining area! The heart of the home lies in the fully updated kitchen, boasting modern appliances and a subway tile backsplash, while the refreshed bathrooms offer a touch of luxury. Outside, a large fenced yard with a storage shed awaits, with newer rocks for maintained landscaping. Noteworthy upgrades, including a brand-new furnace and central air system with all-new ductwork, ensure year-round comfort. Recent updates to the roof, windows, and doors offer peace of mind and energy efficiency. This home seamlessly blends modern amenities with classic charm, making it so homey !!
